---
title: Crumbed Pork Schnitzel & Spiced Wedges with Cherry Tomato Salad & Garlic Aioli
description: The classics have withstood the test of time for a reason and the pork schnitzel with wedges is one of them because what can beat a crunchy crumb? When served with spiced potato wedges and a fresh salad we know that it will be returning to your table many more times.
